1/* $NetBSD: pfilter.c,v 1.7 2019/04/20 17:16:40 christos Exp $ */
2#include "namespace.h"
3#include "includes.h"
4#include "ssh.h"
5#include "packet.h"
6#include "log.h"
7#include "pfilter.h"
8#include <blacklist.h>
9
10#ifndef SMALL
11static struct blacklist *blstate;
12#endif
13
14#include "includes.h"
15__RCSID("$NetBSD: pfilter.c,v 1.7 2019/04/20 17:16:40 christos Exp $");
16
17void
18pfilter_init()
19{
20#ifndef SMALL
21 blstate = blacklist_open();
22#endif
23}
24
25extern struct ssh *the_active_state;
26
27void
28pfilter_notify(int a)
29{
30#ifndef SMALL
31 int fd;
32 if (the_active_state == NULL)
33 return;
34 if (blstate == NULL)
35 pfilter_init();
36 if (blstate == NULL)
37 return;
38 // XXX: 3?
39 fd = ssh_packet_connection_is_on_socket(the_active_state) ?
40 ssh_packet_get_connection_in(the_active_state) : 3;
41 (void)blacklist_r(blstate, a, fd, "ssh");
42 if (a == 0) {
43 blacklist_close(blstate);
44 blstate = NULL;
45 }
46#else
47 __USE(a);
48#endif
49}
